OL,3,CNottingham University urged to
OL,4,Creconsider proposed course suspensions
OL,6,FNottinghamshire MPs have urged the
OL,7,FUniversity of Nottingham to reconsider
OL,8,Fthe suspension of degree courses in
OL,9,Fareas including modern languages,
OL,10,Fnursing and music.
OL,12,FAround 100 students and members of
OL,13,Fstaff gathered on the university
OL,14,Fcampus on Monday afternoon to protest
OL,15,Fagainst the potential closures of
OL,16,Fdozens of degree courses.
