OL,3,CNottingham University urged to
OL,4,Creconsider proposed course suspensions
OL,6,FThe university's council is meeting
OL,7,Ftoday to discuss whether to proceed
OL,8,Fwith the next stage of plans, which
OL,9,Fwould open up engagement with staff,
OL,10,Fstudents and unions about the proposed
OL,11,Fclosures.
OL,13,FStudents currently on the courses have
OL,14,Fbeen told they will be supported to
OL,15,Fcontinue, but the courses facing
OL,16,Fclosure have been suspended for entry
OL,17,Ffor 2026/27.
