OL,3,CNottingham University urged to
OL,4,Creconsider proposed course suspensions
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the University of
OL,7,FNottingham clarified that no decision
OL,8,Fis being made this week about course
OL,9,Fclosures and that the university
OL,10,Fagrees there should be time for
OL,11,Fmeaningful engagement on proposed
OL,12,Fclosures.
OL,14,F"We will now be working with staff,
OL,15,Fstudents, trade unions and other
OL,16,Fstakeholders including our local MPs
OL,17,Fto help shape these proposals," the
OL,18,Fspokesperson said.
