OL,3,CNottingham University urged to
OL,4,Creconsider proposed course suspensions
OL,6,FSeven MPs across the county have
OL,7,Fwritten to the university to support
OL,8,Fcalls from the University and College
OL,9,FUnion (UCU) to immediately pause all
OL,10,Fdegree suspensions.
OL,12,FThe MPs, who include Nadia Whittome,
OL,13,FJuliet Campbell, Lillian Greenwood,
OL,14,FJames Naish, Alex Norris, Michael
OL,15,FPayne, and Michelle Welsh, said the
OL,16,FUCU had raised concerns that there had
OL,17,Fbeen a lack of transparency and proper
OL,18,Fconsultation through the process.
