OL,3,CNottingham University urged to
OL,4,Creconsider proposed course suspensions
OL,6,FThe UCU also raised concerns about the
OL,7,Fmethodology used to decide which
OL,8,Fcourses are suspended, the MPs said.
OL,10,F"We understand the concerns being
OL,11,Fraised by staff, students and trade
OL,12,Funions but the Government has been
OL,13,Fvery clear it expects universities to
OL,14,Fmanage their own finances and focus on
OL,15,Fareas of strength and we are
OL,16,Fresponding to this to ensure the
OL,17,FUniversity of Nottingham remains a
OL,18,Fworld-leading institution long into
OL,19,Fthe future," the university
OL,20,Fspokesperson added.
