OL,3,CNottingham University urged to
OL,4,Creconsider proposed course suspensions
OL,6,FPetitions to stop the course closures
OL,7,Ffor modern languages and music have
OL,8,Fbeen signed by more than 19,000 and
OL,9,Fmore than 15,000 people, respectively.
OL,11,FCharlie Blair, a second-year student
OL,12,Fstudying German and Russian at
OL,13,FNottingham who started the languages
OL,14,Fpetition with a friend, said the
OL,15,Fpotential of closure is "really
OL,16,Fdisappointing".
