OL,3,CNottingham University urged to
OL,4,Creconsider proposed course suspensions
OL,6,FMs Blair, who is in the middle of
OL,7,Fplanning her year abroad as part of
OL,8,Fher course, said students in her year
OL,9,Fhave no idea what they will be coming
OL,10,Fback to in Nottingham when they return.
OL,12,F"A lot of people are worried that in
OL,13,Fthe future, employers will look and
OL,14,Fsee University of Nottingham as your
OL,15,Fdegree and think that that's going to
OL,16,Fmake it seem less valuable," she added.
