OL,3,CNottingham University urged to
OL,4,Creconsider proposed course suspensions
OL,6,FMelanie Bhend, assistant professor in
OL,7,FFrench at the University, said: "I'm a
OL,8,Fbit in limbo, and have no idea what I
OL,9,Fwill be doing come next September.
OL,10,FIt's not easy to keep working in these
OL,11,Fconditions."
OL,13,FPaul Smith, head of the department of
OL,14,Fmodern languages and cultures, said
OL,15,Fthere are around 75 staff members in
OL,16,Fthe department who are "very nervous
OL,17,Fabout their futures".
OL,19,F"There's a great deal of a sense of
OL,20,Finsecurity," he said.
